Reasoning: The paper deals with applications of clustering algorithms in computer vision and pattern recognition, which are the primary focus of the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of graph theory and extensions of dominant set clustering also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the mention of visual geo-localization suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
